creator: Blue Ox Running
descriptionHtml:
Blue Ox Running’s official app is your gateway to our media, events, online store, and your Blue Ox Bux – online & in-store rewards & gift cards!

You're loyal. You shop local, stay active, and should get rewarded for it. We want you to be part of the Blue Ox HERD and earn your Blue Ox Bux! It's simple and free, just download the app and login. Shop in the app or in our store and you'll earn reward points for every dollar you spend. You'll also get reward points for checking in at Blue Ox events. Then redeem those points for Blue Ox Bux – your digital gift cards for in store or online purchases! Plus, track your lifetime point total to level up with reward achievements, bragging rights, and other perks.

Feel like going the extra mile? Take your loyalty a step further by syncing your runs or walks with Strava. Track your mileage to achieve new levels, receive acclaim, or maybe even prizes.

The Blue Ox Running app makes it easy to stay up to date on store news, media, events, sales, and more.

It's easy and free! Simply download the Blue Ox app, log in, and start earning.

Rewards Program – Blue Ox BUX!
• Earn points for every dollar spent pre-tax both in-store and online
• Check-in at participating events to earn extra points
• Points will appear on your account the day after a purchase is made
• Redeem Points for Blue Ox digital gift cards redeemable both in-store and online
• Easily keep track of your points and redemptions right in your app

Strava Integration - Blue Ox Miles Program!
• Sync your Strava Runs and walks to track your mileage in the app
• Stay motivated by unlocking achievements when distance milestones are reached
